font-sans.fontFamily: Arimo, Helvetica, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"

font-mono.fontFamily: Comic Mono, Cousine, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace

transform.transform: translateX(var(--transform-translate-x)) translateY(var(--transform-translate-y)) rotate(var(--transform-rotate)) skewX(var(--transform-skew-x)) skewY(var(--transform-skew-y)) scaleX(var(--transform-scale-x)) scaleY(var(--transform-scale-y))
